         <abstract id="aspace_85cc7c5f9ed8109442c4aef970efcdce">Letters, reports, and printed material document the work of the Peking (Beijing) YMCA, which was sponsored by Princeton-in-Peking. Lennig Sweet served the YMCA in Beijing, China between 1916 and 1934. He later worked for United China Relief from 1942 to 1947 and as YMCA Secretary for Overseas Staff and YMCA Secretary in Seoul, Korea.</abstract>
